Here are the main functionalities of your weather app:

1.Current Weather Display – Shows the current temperature, weather conditions (e.g., sunny, rainy, snowy), and other relevant details.
2.City Search – Allows users to enter a city name and view the weather for that location.
3.Detailed Weather Data – Provides additional details like humidity, wind speed, and more.
4.Modern UI – A clean and user-friendly interface for easy navigation.
5.Possible API integration – Uses a weather API to fetch real-time information.


